Package com.amazonaws.mobileconnectors.lex.interactionkit.internal.audio

Class ChunkedAudioStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.mobileconnectors.lex.interactionkit.internal.audio.AudioStream
      • com.amazonaws.mobileconnectors.lex.interactionkit.internal.audio.ChunkedAudioStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AudioSource, ChunkedAudioSource
    public class ChunkedAudioStream
extends AudioStream
implements ChunkedAudioSource
    An AudioSource that writes a stream of audio to the network connection in chunks. Currently only audio/x-l16, audio/x-l16preamble, and audio/x-cbr-opus-preamble are supported.
